  "prompt": "Where can I found a large range of formal and evening wear in Gold Coast?",
  "response": "If you're looking for a large range of formal and evening wear in the Gold Coast, there are several stores and shopping destinations you can explore:\n\n### **Shopping Centers:**\n1. **Pacific Fair Shopping Centre** (Broadbeach):  \n   - Home to a variety of high-end and designer brands like Myer, David Jones, Forever New, and Witchery, which offer formal and evening wear.  \n   - Also has boutique stores and international brands for stylish options.\n\n2. **Robina Town Centre** (Robina):  \n   - Features stores like Myer, DJs, and specialty boutiques that cater to formal and evening attire.\n\n### **Boutiques and Specialty Stores:**\n1. **Marquee by Veronica May** (Broadbeach):  \n   - A boutique offering a curated selection of formal and evening dresses. Perfect for events, weddings, and galas.\n\n2. **Saba** (Pacific Fair and Robina Town Centre):  \n   - Known for elegant, contemporary designs suitable for formal occasions.\n\n3. **Bec + Bridge** (Pacific Fair):  \n   - Offers chic and modern evening wear.\n\n4. **Forever New** (Pacific Fair and Robina Town Centre):  \n   - A popular choice for sophisticated dresses and formal outfits.\n\n### **Bridal and Event Wear:**\n1. **The Bridal Atelier** (Mermaid Beach):  \n   - Specializes in formal and bridal wear, offering stunning gowns for special occasions.\n\n2. **Stella York** (Broadbeach):  \n   - Offers evening and formal gowns with a focus on elegance and sophistication.\n\n### **Designer Stores:**\n1. **Camilla** (Pacific Fair):  \n   - Known for bold, luxurious designs perfect for formal events.\n\n2. **Politix** (Pacific Fair):  \n   - A great option for men\u2019s formal wear, including suits and evening attire.\n\n### **Online Options (with Local Presence):**\n1. **Showpo** (Online with local shipping):  \n   - Offers trendy and affordable formal and evening wear.\n\n2. **The Iconic** (Online with fast shipping):  \n   - Features a wide range of designer and contemporary formal wear.\n\n### **Outlet Shopping:**\n1. **Harbour Town Outlet Shopping Centre** (Biggera Waters):  \n   - Offers discounted formal and evening wear from brands like Farage, Marcs, and Forever New.\n\n### **Tailoring and Custom Options:**\n1. **Godwin Charli** (Broadbeach):  \n   - A designer boutique offering custom-made formal and evening wear.\n\n2. **MJ Bale** (Pacific Fair):  \n   - Specializes in tailored suits and formal wear for men.\n\nThese locations and stores should provide you with a wide variety of options for formal and evening wear on the Gold Coast. It\u2019s always a good idea to call ahead or check their websites for current collections and availability.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
